    "name": "Driftlure",
    "type": "alien",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "The coarse cilia that cover this large, pale crustacean undulate with bioluminescence. A driftlure attacks by attaching to the hull of a starship, where it emits a powerful psychic blast, luring the crew into space. The driftlure then collects the choicest specimens (often still clawing for breath in the vacuum) and nestles them amongst its cilia as macabre decorations. Its motivations remain unknown."
        }
    ],
